OL,3,CNew #319m plan to reverse community
OL,4,Cdecline across UK
OL,6,FNew funding to boost high streets and
OL,7,Fimprove public spaces will help to
OL,8,Freverse the decline of local
OL,9,Fcommunities, the government hopes.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,12,Fand Local Government has pledged #319
OL,13,Fmillion to "restore pride and
OL,14,Fopportunity in neighbourhoods across
OL,15,Fthe country".
OL,17,FCommunities Secretary Steve Reed said
OL,18,Fpeople have watched their communities
OL,19,Fdecline "for too long".
OL,26,@uD@LOUwD@LO]{D@IOU{D@VO]
