OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774180969
OL,3,CNew #319m plan to reverse community
OL,4,Cdecline across UK
OL,6,F"This government is determined to
OL,7,Fchange that ` giving communities the
OL,8,Ftools, the funding and the power they
OL,9,Fneed to rebuild," he added.
OL,11,F"From new playgrounds to reimagined
OL,12,Fhigh streets, we're putting power back
OL,13,Fin people's hands. People across the
OL,14,Fcountry will see and feel the
OL,15,Fdifference this investment makes,
OL,16,Frestoring pride in local areas."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]sD@AOUxD@`O]
