OL,3,CNew #319m plan to reverse community
OL,4,Cdecline across UK
OL,6,FReed announced #20 million in funding
OL,7,Ffor 40 communities in England on
OL,8,FFriday where he insisted the
OL,9,Fannouncement, seven weeks before May's
OL,10,Felections, was not a pre-election bung
OL,11,Faimed at wavering votes.
OL,13,FOn Friday, Reed said ministers are
OL,14,Ftrying to help areas that were "held
OL,15,Fback the most under the Conservatives".
OL,17,FHe added: "This is a rolling programme
OL,18,Fthat Labour introduced as soon as we
OL,19,Fwon the general election.
OL,26,@vD@`OUwD@fO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
