OL,3,CNew #319m plan to reverse community
OL,4,Cdecline across UK
OL,6,F"What we're trying to do is give those
OL,7,Fareas that were held back the most
OL,8,Funder the Conservatives the chance to
OL,9,Fmake a difference on their own terms,
OL,10,Fto put pride back into those
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FFunding under the Pride in Place
OL,19,Fprogramme includes:
